- Mm-hm.

577
00:49:42,408 --> 00:49:44,776
Vera i sujeverje.

578
00:49:44,909 --> 00:49:46,475
Znaš, prvog dana bio sam ovde,

579
00:49:46,609 --> 00:49:49,375
